Where to place it (HTML): insert this **between** the closing `</section>` of **Why Choose …** and the opening `<section … id="secondary-maths-topics">` (i.e., right before the Topics section). fileciteturn0file0

```html
<!-- ===== Timetable & Booking ===== -->
<section class="section section--schedule" id="timetable" aria-labelledby="schedule-title">
  <h2 class="section-title" id="schedule-title">Small-Group Timetable &amp; Booking</h2>

  <div class="schedule-wrap">
    <!-- Timetable card -->
    <article class="schedule-card" role="region" aria-labelledby="schedule-title">
      <p class="lead">E&nbsp;Maths &amp; A&nbsp;Maths small-group classes.</p>

      <div class="slot">
        <h3>Weekdays <span class="muted">(Tue–Fri)</span></h3>
        <ul class="time-list" aria-label="Weekday times">
          <li class="time-chip">3:00&nbsp;pm</li>
          <li class="time-chip">5:00&nbsp;pm</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="slot">
        <h3>Saturday</h3>
        <ul class="time-list" aria-label="Saturday times">
          <li class="time-chip">9:30&nbsp;am</li>
          <li class="time-chip">11:30&nbsp;am</li>
          <li class="time-chip">2:00&nbsp;pm</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="slot">
        <h3>Sunday</h3>
        <ul class="time-list" aria-label="Sunday times">
          <li class="time-chip">9:30&nbsp;am</li>
          <li class="time-chip">11:30&nbsp;am</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p class="fineprint">Slots subject to availability; contact to confirm.</p>
    </article>

    <!-- CTA card (reuses the Contact pill buttons styling) -->
    <aside class="schedule-cta" aria-label="Book or enquire">
      <h3 class="cta-title">Book a trial or ask a question</h3>
      <p class="cta-blurb">Fastest: WhatsApp. Or use the contact form below.</p>
      <div class="actions">
        <a class="btn-pill" href="https://wa.me/6592997306?text=Hello.%20"
           target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp +65&nbsp;9299&nbsp;7306</a>
        <a class="btn-pill" href="#contact">Contact Form</a>
      </div>
      <p class="cta-meta">Location: 5-minute walk from Kovan MRT.</p>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>
```

